metadata.name: Portrait of a Dreamer
metadata.description: Portrait of a woman who has lived in dreams all her life. This woman, whose life is very boring, has been coloring her life with the dreams she has had since her childhood. This woman, who has always dreamed of living happily and peacefully in a place where the sky, sea, mountains and forests meet, among colorful flowers and butterflies, unfortunately, has always lived with these dreams from her childhood until her old age. This design is a work that keeps his dreams alive.
